OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, HSBC has become the latest big company 
OL,6, to announce a shift to more casual     
OL,7, uniforms for 4,000 branch staff.       
OL,9,FThe new range includes jumpsuits and   
OL,10,F"menopause-friendly" garments for      
OL,11,Fwomen, ethnic-wear, including tunics   
OL,12,Fand hijabs, and chinos and jeans.      
OL,14,FLast month, British Airways unveiled   
OL,15,Fits first new uniform for 20 years,    
OL,16,Fincluding a jumpsuit for female ground 
OL,17,Fstaff and cabin crew.                  
OL,19,FHSBC is to close 114 more UK branches  
OL,20,Ffrom April, with about 100 jobs going. 
